name: This World Is Not For Us
description:
Thank you for your interest in my photographs :) All prints are hand packaged with mass amounts of love and care! Each print is titled, numbered and signed on the back. All prints also come with a white border unless requested otherwise. 

My fine art photos are limited edition prints of 100. Meaning I will no longer print a photo once I've sold 100 of them. This is your opportunity to own a beautiful photograph that only 99 other people could have! Narrowing it down further, metallic prints of each photo are limited editions of 10 (add $20 to price).

Please allow up to two weeks for shipping and processing. 

Keep in mind not all of my photos are featured here. You can visit my portfolio and other social media sites to view more. Feel free to contact me with any questions or custom orders. And again, thank you so much!
